00:00:24.271 --> 00:00:26.480
I told him he could finish inside.

00:00:27.105 --> 00:00:29.230
Shizuku, since you got those tattoos,

00:00:29.313 --> 00:00:31.105
it's hard to find clients.

00:00:31.813 --> 00:00:34.230
I managed to get a customer
for 10,000 an hour.

00:00:35.855 --> 00:00:39.396
Oh, and from now on,
go ahead and find your own customers.

00:00:50.605 --> 00:00:52.188
10,000 yen.

00:00:52.855 --> 00:00:54.021
I'll do my best.

