00:02:28.896 --> 00:02:30.105
That's enough.

00:02:31.855 --> 00:02:34.063
It's all good now.

00:02:43.938 --> 00:02:46.396
I'm so pissed.

00:02:47.563 --> 00:02:49.396
I'm going to work.

00:02:50.355 --> 00:02:52.355
Stay here, okay?

00:03:01.313 --> 00:03:04.521
I get anxious when Mu's not around.

00:03:14.646 --> 00:03:16.938
I can't stay calm
unless I'm eating something.

00:03:51.021 --> 00:03:53.480
I ate too much again.

00:03:55.105 --> 00:03:58.188
If I get fat, Shuto's going to hate me.

00:04:05.688 --> 00:04:07.771
Every second, I feel like I want to die.

00:04:08.771 --> 00:04:11.480
I'm being crushed by loneliness.

00:04:12.438 --> 00:04:17.813
I'm lonely. I feel so lonely
that I can't stand it.

00:04:21.646 --> 00:04:22.980
Somebody

00:04:23.938 --> 00:04:25.480
help me.

00:04:37.396 --> 00:04:39.313
Mu.

00:04:41.063 --> 00:04:42.438
Shizuku.

00:04:49.230 --> 00:04:55.855
Let's drink some hot water,
brush our teeth, and go to bed together.

00:04:58.563 --> 00:04:59.688
Okay.

00:05:04.521 --> 00:05:05.938
Let's eat.

00:05:16.521 --> 00:05:19.021
It's rare for you to order eel for me.

00:05:19.105 --> 00:05:20.105
Is it?

00:05:20.605 --> 00:05:24.730
I just have this image of you
eating nothing but junk food.

00:05:24.813 --> 00:05:26.771
Junk food?

00:05:28.230 --> 00:05:32.396
Like takoyaki, which claims to be
the best in Japan, or cup noodles.

00:05:33.563 --> 00:05:36.563
Or what was it?
That bizarre chunk of meat.

00:05:37.105 --> 00:05:38.896
They're all as good as eel.

00:05:38.980 --> 00:05:40.396
Well, anyway,

00:05:40.896 --> 00:05:43.313
I guess you and Attorney Kameoka
are now tied.

