and her video was pulled.

00:05:55.271 --> 00:05:56.855
So Attorney Kameoka won.

00:06:01.105 --> 00:06:02.688
And did you see this?

00:06:04.896 --> 00:06:06.896
It says, "Joan of Arc of the legal world

00:06:06.980 --> 00:06:11.730
saves Shizuku Pien and exposes
exploitative system in the AV industry."

00:06:15.605 --> 00:06:19.396
Anyway, you've resolved
Mr. Kyogoku's case,

00:06:19.896 --> 00:06:21.396
so this is it from him, right?

00:06:23.855 --> 00:06:25.938
Nothing's resolved yet.

00:06:27.146 --> 00:06:27.980
What?

00:06:34.230 --> 00:06:35.438
I'm scared.

00:06:35.521 --> 00:06:37.771
I'm scared of people looking at me.

00:06:38.771 --> 00:06:40.021
In the morning,

00:06:40.105 --> 00:06:44.855
I feel miserable when I pass by
people going to work or school

00:06:44.938 --> 00:06:46.355
because I have nothing.

00:06:47.313 --> 00:06:51.605
I'm sorry such a shabby person
like me exists here.

00:06:53.271 --> 00:06:58.230
If I'm going to hurt someone,
I'd rather hurt myself.

00:06:58.980 --> 00:07:03.980
More than anything,
I want money so I can meet Shuto.

00:07:07.688 --> 00:07:09.313
Ao.

00:07:09.813 --> 00:07:14.980
Ao! I want to come back
to the AV industry. Please!

00:07:15.521 --> 00:07:16.771
Don't be ridiculous.

00:07:16.855 --> 00:07:19.688
Do you know how much trouble
you've put us through?

00:07:20.313 --> 00:07:23.521
I'm sorry!

00:07:23.605 --> 00:07:25.188
Shut up.

00:07:25.271 --> 00:07:28.438
I told you I'd call the police
if you came back again. Leave.

00:07:29.605 --> 00:07:32.646
I'm sorry!

00:07:32.730 --> 00:07:33.855
What's wrong with you?

00:07:33.938 --> 00:07:36.980
I'm sorry.

00:07:37.063 --> 00:07:38.146
Hello?

00:07:38.938 --> 00:07:42.980
Oh, Madoka! I was waiting for your call.

00:07:43.480 --> 00:07:47.521
What? You're going to appear
in our work? I'm thrilled.

00:07:47.605 --> 00:07:49.688
Someone like you should…

00:08:05.896 --> 00:08:07.271
Is everything okay?

00:08:12.105 --> 00:08:13.230
Who are you?

00:08:24.521 --> 00:08:26.355
I'm Attorney Kujo.

00:08:27.605 --> 00:08:29.521
Please contact me if anything happens.

00:08:39.896 --> 00:08:43.021
Attorney… Kujo.

00:08:50.688 --> 00:08:52.980
-I'm home.
-Welcome back.

00:08:53.063 --> 00:08:54.646
I got anmitsu today.

00:08:54.730 --> 00:08:56.813
Anmitsu? I love it!

00:08:57.396 --> 00:08:59.521
-I'll make some tea. Have a seat.
-Okay.

00:09:13.313 --> 00:09:17.021
ANMITSU

00:09:31.021 --> 00:09:32.230
Shinji.

00:09:33.688 --> 00:09:36.188
How's work?

00:09:36.271 --> 00:09:38.563
Oh, I'm busy with a lot of things.

00:09:38.646 --> 00:09:41.063
My current office
has only the two of us working.

00:09:41.146 --> 00:09:44.563
Attorney Kujo takes on cases
for people with problematic backgrounds.

00:09:47.605 --> 00:09:49.355
This Attorney Kujo

00:09:50.355 --> 00:09:53.146
is known as a crooked lawyer, isn't he?

00:09:54.605 --> 00:09:56.188
I saw it on the Internet.

00:09:59.355 --> 00:10:00.480
Hey.

00:10:02.021 --> 00:10:05.230
Is Attorney Kujo really
the kind of person everyone says he is?

00:10:06.480 --> 00:10:09.188
There are probably
quite a few people who think that.

00:10:10.896 --> 00:10:13.688
Are you sure it's okay
to be working for Attorney Kujo?

00:10:14.188 --> 00:10:19.063
Hey, you've finally become an attorney.
Won't you get involved in something bad?

00:10:19.146 --> 00:10:21.896
I'll be fine. I'm being careful.

00:10:23.021 --> 00:10:24.730
I'm going to enjoy this.

00:10:29.521 --> 00:10:30.855
That's good to hear.

00:10:34.855 --> 00:10:38.355
But being an attorney must be hard.

00:10:39.771 --> 00:10:43.896
Sometimes you have to defend bad people.

00:10:44.646 --> 00:10:47.063
That's an attorney's duty.

00:10:47.146 --> 00:10:50.980
Someone has to follow
the correct criminal procedures.

00:10:52.355 --> 00:10:54.813
When you save one,

00:10:55.313 --> 00:10:57.230
you bring sorrow to another.

00:11:01.938 --> 00:11:03.521
Attorney Kujo…

00:11:04.438 --> 00:11:05.646
I wonder how he feels…

00:11:07.480 --> 00:11:10.688
