I wonder, as an attorney,
am I really helping people?

00:13:02.938 --> 00:13:05.813
What does it mean to help others?

00:13:12.688 --> 00:13:14.896
10,000, not including the room.

00:13:15.396 --> 00:13:17.438
How scary. Damn!

