see the other person.

00:22:00.146 --> 00:22:03.230
Why do you talk like that?
The way you talk gets on my nerves.

00:22:03.313 --> 00:22:06.355
I absolutely don't want
to be lectured one bit by a man

00:22:06.438 --> 00:22:09.146
